com.microsoft.windowsazure.management.network

Interface NetworkSecurityGroupOperations

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NetworkSecurityGroupOperationsImpl

    public interface NetworkSecurityGroupOperations
    The Network Management API includes operations for managing the Network Security Groups for your subscription.
